============================================
|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME|EST. ROWS|COST|
--------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN DISTR  |    |0        |0   |
|1 | EXCHANGE OUT DISTR|    |0        |0   |
|2 |  INSERT           |    |0        |0   |
|3 |   EXPRESSION      |    |0        |0   |
============================================

